Packages 
Package Description
Client
Client classes for the MEME generator application Package contains controllers for different scenes of application, main class (ClientMain), ActiveSession class that stores information about current session (username, downloaded memes, etc) and MyImageView class to display memes in generator correctly FXML Files used to generate GUI are stored in resources as well as sample memes' images and other graphics
Client.Exceptions
Custom exceptions
GeneralClasses
Generic classes used by both client and server for the MEME generator application Package contains Meme class used to store meme image and all additional information needed like bottom and upper text, tag, author or title.
Server
Server classes for the MEME generator application Package contains Server class that uses thread poll to handle client request, WorkerRunnable class that handles one specific request and DB class that sends SQL requests to database.
